{"tid":363034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血時報老闆娘：黃之鋒已好慘　多一個都太多　不要鬥慘　更不落井下石","createTime":"2017-08-17T10:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T04:46:20.000Z","uid":47714,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e1f0c9a52c5e853f4f8f18f8c10905e0752819","tid":363034,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sausau/posts/10155144015698173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsausau%2Fposts%2F10155144015698173&d=0P7hoSPHAgNgNo%2F2AEExBdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3e265c2f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/sausau/posts/10155144015698173</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：SauWai Chan<br />\n<br />\n唔係要鬥慘，更加唔係落井下石，囚徒困苦無可能唔知，我地身邊已經太多人受過，甚至受緊..... 切膚之痛，多一個都太多。<br />\n不過現在香港環境唔係一朝一日變成，你地跟著蘋果老泛民的指揮棒看待香港，永遠都看不見真相、跟不上局勢變化、來不及做準備。<br />\n雨傘革命的根本唔係浪漫激情，唔係愛與和平，政治，對肥佬黎那一代影響者來說，不過一場虛妄，一些口號，一種霸權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sausau/posts/10155143938383173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsausau%2Fposts%2F10155143938383173&d=0P7hoSPHAgNgNo%2F2AEExBdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ad8ea43e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/sausau/posts/10155143938383173</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：SauWai Chan<br />\n<br />\n六個月，七個月，八個月....<br />\n唉，黃之峰最慘，被判監三個月以上，五年內不能參選.....<br />\n五年咩世界唔知，其實半年後都好難知....<br />\n不過呢個環境，其實早三四年已經預言咗.... 不過冇人信...呀唔係，係肥佬黎一個唔信就搞到咁。<br />\n<br />\nHoi Fung So:<br />\n刑期嘅目的其中一個就係令佢地參加唔到＂補選＂，完全係政治凌駕司法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sausau/posts/10155144030418173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsausau%2Fposts%2F10155144030418173&d=0P7hoSPHAgNgNo%2F2AEExBdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ec6dd937\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/sausau/posts/10155144030418173</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：SauWai Chan<br />\n<br />\n難受都不及受者親人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sausau/posts/10155143803638173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsausau%2Fposts%2F10155143803638173&d=0P7hoSPHAgNgNo%2F2AEExBdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b85eb008\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/sausau/posts/10155143803638173</a><br />\n<br />\nAlvin Chu King Long: 其實係咪我哋走路太快？<br />\n<br />\nSauWai Chan: 呢幾年環境變得幾快先得，要求一般人跟得上真係好苛刻。"},{"pid":"84f226af6013008e32fc3b2c5bf0117465b4126e","tid":363034,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8895/28198463512_7655922340_b_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm9.staticflickr.com%2F8895%2F28198463512_7655922340_b_d.jpg&h=a2cd63eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c6ad93202a576d63899db9b140d8857945829d9","tid":363034,"uid":53687,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"無用架啦，熱狗作孽太多，唔會靠講返幾句人話就洗到底。"},{"pid":"7a220dd16b5990112e303992b61e702241988257","tid":363034,"uid":103230,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:05:54.000Z","msg":"由你把口講出黎真係好有說服力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f908364fb7233986baa1e14d54a3b5a6649ac526","tid":363034,"uid":130079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Quote熱血加返 利申唔該<br />\n<br />\n唔係好難搵邊個係正常人<br />\n正常人同熱血係割開/無關係<br />\n<br />\n利申：熱血正垃圾 </span></span>"},{"pid":"ea9dc1ce3d2375cd99fb15886312255b2a3abae6","tid":363034,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱狗咪又係支那人<br />\n搞咁多做咩撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{